Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,commercial grade music production
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to your local machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen For Free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking generation times
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that would make traditional
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,door producers, weep, quality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,scores that rival major
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,labels, and a completely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,open architecture
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that means you're not
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,locked into some subscription
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,service.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,open source music generation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has been building toward,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to
