Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,prompt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and transforms it into
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a comprehensive song blueprint,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,handling everything from structure
